        {
            "title": "亞洲雄厚的外匯存底足以抵禦本幣貶值 多國央行已介入市場",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 隨著中東戰事升溫推高能源價格，亞洲各國央行握有的8萬億美元外匯存底，成為捍衛本幣的重要「火力」。對高度依賴石油進口的亞洲經濟體而言，油價飆升構成關鍵風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印尼、印度與台灣已介入市場，中國則透過上調每日人民幣中間價釋出穩匯訊號。其他國家當局目前多停留在口頭警告階段，同時密切關注市場波動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著投資人評估油價上漲對進口成本、通膨、經濟成長與財政收支的衝擊，亞洲貨幣普遍承壓。若匯率急貶，恐引發資本外流。本周，印度盧比跌至紀錄低點，韓元跌至全球金融危機以來的最低水平，印尼盾則跌至六周以來的最低點。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4000fac9-0808-3c7f-94b5-8f4ff49b90ad-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Emkay Global Financial Services Ltd.首席經濟學家Madhavi Arora表示，匯率穩定是金融穩定的錨。當市場出現大量投機部位時，往往對宏觀經濟與市場產生超出基本面的負向回饋效應，因此各國央行必須嚴陣以待。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kn.2C503O9ZaxYiPKq3Q_g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a034de98c5fbec26b2181726e7d29009\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據彭博計算，亞洲主要央行的外匯存底自2024年底以來已增加約6,000億美元。過去一年，當局持續吸納資金流入，加上金價上漲與美元走弱，也推升了外匯存底的價值。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印尼央行高級副總裁Destry Damayanti周三表示，印尼正在干預外匯市場，將在離岸無本金交割遠期(NDF)、在岸NDF、現貨與債市持續「堅定且一致地」進場操作 。惠譽當天稍晚將印尼的信用評等展望下調至「負向」，理由是政策不確定性升高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">駐孟買的交易員表示，印度央行一直在賣出美元，此舉旨在支撐印度盧比，此前該貨幣已跌至紀錄低點。台灣央行外匯局局長蔡烱民周四在記者會上表示，本周在外資匯出金額比較大的時候，央行有進場調節。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Robust Asian Reserve Pile Positioned to Defend Currency Slide</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E9%9B%84%E5%8E%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AF%E5%AD%98%E5%BA%95%E8%B6%B3%E4%BB%A5%E6%8A%B5%E7%A6%A6%E6%9C%AC%E5%B9%A3%E8%B2%B6%E5%80%BC-%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%B7%B2%E4%BB%8B%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-004125064.html",
