            "title": "今日我咁睇｜京東業績有驚喜 中資科網料反彈 港股料25000築底｜小編苟豪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XqwJQ4XVrnpx_kuFDpWpPQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/987bae8f26649e86d9ba371f0ed4f0c0\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">1.近日所有分析都離不開伊朗，暫時沒有新進展，有消息指美軍可能預期要打長期戰，雖然小編偏向估計不會，但美股就相當恐慌，油價亦創近年新高，短期美股尚未見一個比較大的反彈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2.與此同時，京東公佈業績，雖然加入燒錢大軍，但盈利勝市場預期，且屬預期範圍的上限，令市場對科網特別是電商股的悲觀情緒有所減少。之前怕燒錢燒出火，但暫時來看後果不太嚴重，今日京東、阿里及美團等應有反彈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3. 暫時來看，油價仍然難測，與油價相關的股份，不論受惠或受累的，現階段有點賭大細的味道，還是小心為上。如果博指數超跌反彈，可以考慮內地金融或本地地產股。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7377584e-7c14-33ba-bbbb-b1187fdaf01d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4. 港股短期於25200點及25000點應有支持，阻力位維持在25500點及25800點，上26000點恐怕要等多一兩星期。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5. 恒指牛熊證街貨比例，牛證街貨水平為61%，較之前大幅回落，若跌穿六成則可能有機會夾熊。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E6%88%91%E5%92%81%E7%9D%87-%E4%BA%AC%E6%9D%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%B8%BE%E6%9C%89%E9%A9%9A%E5%96%9C-%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E7%A7%91%E7%B6%B2%E6%96%99%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88-%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E6%96%9925000%E7%AF%89%E5%BA%95-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B7%A8%E8%8B%9F%E8%B1%AA-020000281.html",
